---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Careers | Kaya Blue" description="Join the Kaya Blue team.">
<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative pt-48 pb-32 px-8 overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-lowest">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-surface-container-low opacity-50 -z-10 transform skew-x-12 translate-x-32"></div>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-10 lg:col-span-8 text-left">
<span class="text-secondary font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[10px] mb-6 block">Career Opportunities</span>
<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-12">
                            Join the <span class="text-primary">Architects</span> of the Digital Frontier
                        </h1>
<p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
                            We are building the structural backbone of tomorrow's web. High-performance logic meets architectural precision.
                        </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Open Positions Section (Bento Grid) -->
<section class="py-24 px-8 bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-end mb-16 gap-4">
<div class="text-left">
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-on-surface">Open Positions</h2>
<p class="text-secondary tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mt-2">Precision roles for technical minds</p>
</div>
<div class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium text-sm">
                        Filter by: <span class="text-primary underline ml-2 cursor-pointer">All Roles</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-1">
<!-- Role Card 1 -->
<div class="group bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-between hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-300 text-left">
<div>
<span class="text-secondary group-hover:text-on-primary text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Engineering</span>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-4 mb-2 group-hover:text-on-primary">Senior Systems Architect</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant group-hover:text-on-primary/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">Design and scale distributed infrastructure for global architectural platforms.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-between">
<span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-tighter group-hover:text-on-primary">REMOTE / FULL-TIME</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:text-on-primary transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-2">arrow_forward</span>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Role Card 2 -->
<div class="group bg-surface-container-low p-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-between hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-300 text-left">
<div>
<span class="text-secondary group-hover:text-on-primary text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Design</span>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-4 mb-2 group-hover:text-on-primary">Creative Lead</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant group-hover:text-on-primary/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">Define the visual language of high-performance architectural systems.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-between">
<span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-tighter group-hover:text-on-primary">LONDON / HYBRID</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:text-on-primary transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-2">arrow_forward</span>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Role Card 3 -->
<div class="group bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-between hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-300 text-left">
<div>
<span class="text-secondary group-hover:text-on-primary text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Engineering</span>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-4 mb-2 group-hover:text-on-primary">Full-Stack Engineer</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant group-hover:text-on-primary/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">Architect seamless bridges between complex backend logic and pixel-perfect UIs.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-between">
<span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-tighter group-hover:text-on-primary">REMOTE / FULL-TIME</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:text-on-primary transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-2">arrow_forward</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Perks Section (Asymmetric) -->
<section class="py-32 px-8 bg-surface-container-low">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-24 items-center">
<div class="relative order-2 md:order-1">
<div class="aspect-square bg-surface-container-highest flex items-center justify-center p-12">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center" data-alt="Modern architectural workspace with high ceilings and light" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDN-pNDbWC-qWnLcjVtMkYvfQYwj88MVSvfdyr1ntwUyjHoJK62_NrIsWeSIM_eG4sAmVw-10LuJarqpuBZotAEep0t8BmRdkOoylnq7l0w8KjN4jELmi4dzOLeAuPro2_UKGbMEzG8NqnilYraM7cakYmF5plqx7Y123q9JOF4sYTxx5SLQZ5JJ--nfx5YvcizDZJLl7zWNxJQXSBwFER64Ougjw-MUyn0ZyA97MVkveVfyXvdOZ4F5yor7I_F9lJhB4-O7Hft9ms')"></div>
</div>
<div class="absolute -bottom-12 -right-12 bg-primary p-12 hidden md:block">
<span class="text-on-primary text-5xl font-black">2024</span>
<p class="text-on-primary text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold mt-2">Peak Innovation</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="order-1 md:order-2 text-left">
<h2 class="text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-16 leading-none">Designed for Mastery</h2>
<div class="space-y-12">
<div class="flex gap-6">
<span class="text-primary font-black text-2xl">01</span>
<div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Remote-First</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Work from anywhere. Our infrastructure is built for seamless global collaboration without borders.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-6">
<span class="text-primary font-black text-2xl">02</span>
<div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">High-Performance Stack</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">No legacy debt. We use the most advanced tools to build the most resilient systems in the industry.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-6">
<span class="text-primary font-black text-2xl">03</span>
<div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Professional Mastery</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Weekly workshops and annual mastery stipends to ensure you remain at the frontier of your craft.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Culture Section -->
<section class="py-40 px-8 bg-surface-container-lowest">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-left">
<span class="text-secondary font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] mb-8 block">Our Philosophy</span>
<blockquote class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-tight max-w-5xl italic mb-16">
                    "We don't just build sites; <br/> we build <span class="text-primary underline decoration-4 underline-offset-8">revenue engines</span>."
                </blockquote>
<div class="h-1 w-24 bg-primary mb-16"></div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    At Kaya Blue, we treat code like physical steel. Every line must serve a structural purpose. Every pixel must drive performance. We are looking for engineers and designers who obsess over the 'why' as much as the 'how'.
                </p>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="py-24 px-8 bg-on-primary-container">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-12">
<div class="text-left">
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-on-primary tracking-tight mb-4">Ready to architect the future?</h2>
<p class="text-primary-fixed/60 font-medium">Don't see a role that fits? We're always looking for exceptional talent.</p>
</div>
<a href="/book-a-call" class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-12 py-5 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:bg-primary-container transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">Send Spontaneous Application</a>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</BaseLayout>
